48\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-guide-1066x1440.jpg 1066w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104148\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-guide-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104148\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-guide.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-chilling-nazi-history\"><strong>Chilling Nazi History<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The turbulent history began in World War 2 when the Nazis seized the castle from the Hochberg&#x2019;s. It was even rumored that <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Adolf_Hitler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Hitler<\/a> would relocate and make the Ksiaz Castle his headquarters. The true mystery is the network of underground tunnels built by the Nazis during this time. No one knows why these tunnels were created (named the Riese Project), but it&#x2019;s said they were going to be used for secret Nazi operations.  <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Must-read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/auschwitz-birkenau\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Auschwitz Concentration Camp<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-1080x719.jpg\" alt=\"poland most beautiful castle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"poland most beautiful castle\" class=\"wp-image-50192 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-1440x959.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104129\/most-beautiful-castle-1080x719.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Now visitors have the chance to explore 1.5 km of tunnels carved out of the rock face and reinforced with concrete. There are even the remnants of an elevator shaft that apparently led to Hitler&#x2019;s bedroom. These fascinating tunnels give visitors the chance to learn about the turbulent history of the castle, as well as the myths and secrets.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ksiaz-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book the Ksiaz Hotel<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/49814&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104122\/Ksiaz-Castle-poland.