             <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also discover:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/wroclaw\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wroclaw, Poland<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-where-to-stay\">Where to Stay<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want the real fairytale experience, book a stay at Ksiaz Castle itself! Situated within the wooded grounds, in three castle outbuildings, is the Ksiaz Hotel. It&#x2019;s a beautiful hotel and a great place to stay to relax and enjoy the surroundings after a long day at the castle. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re taking part in the &#x2018;Ksiaz by night&#x2019; tour, stay at the hotel to save yourself making a journey back to Wroclaw late at night.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ksiaz-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book the Ksiaz Hotel<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel.jpg\" alt=\"Ksiaz Castle Poland hotel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Ksiaz Castle Poland hotel\" class=\"wp-image-50188 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-1152x1440.jpg 1152w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104143\/Ksiaz-Castle-Poland-hotel-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png